en locals to catch up with all the stuff."},{"pid":"61613e3369f841071abe7a81d41795ee6fcd6363","tid":1639203,"uid":89045,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T17:56:27.000Z","msg":"開時事台叫人去twitter promote lihkg world"},{"pid":"fbb1d661160de07a2095a0936197160bbb60e5df","tid":1639203,"uid":9448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T22:07:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fc2cf9e3cf77e0f803bfe403088f8d684800c880","tid":1639203,"uid":249705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T23:48:30.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f4985a47b1a279f0bf37fed0d2ddc57351f46812","tid":1639203,"uid":313893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T00:12:56.000Z","msg":"唔係咁同意外國人無渠道睇香港既片Twitter 大把<br />\n<br />\n我覺得真正有用既係吸納唔識中文既「連登仔」。好似我地去reddit 一樣。<br />\n<br />\n個人意見，唔洗刻意。大家日日返來用外文出post。正正經經咁做新聞台，從來都唔係我地強項。<br />\n<br />\n不過同意要令呢度有用，必須有高質既post，見到有值得分享既post 就share 去twitter，大家一齊努力。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58bc71bb74c814342ebd9f2fa83df4540a333b1d","tid":1639203,"uid":296108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T00:25:03.000Z","msg":"不過同意要令呢度有用，必須有高質既post，見到有值得分享既post 就share 去twitter，大家一齊努力。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fba33be61ee1217306826a2c1e4f140b8fd0a8e0","tid":1639203,"uid":151057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"58bc71bb74c814342ebd9f2fa83df4540a333b1d","tid":1639203,"uid":296108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T00:25:03.000Z","msg":"不過同意要令呢度有用，必須有高質既post，見到有值得分享既post 就share 去twitter，大家一齊努力。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:03:04.000Z","msg":"你唔記得轉AC喎<br />\n<br />\nBTW 新聞台就係想要出高質post"},{"pid":"80c9bc9a7887cf9edfd726f965f256312b083198","tid":1639203,"uid":151057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:03:46.000Z","msg":"所謂新聞台